OL,6,FViolence flared after an an anti-
OL,7,Fimmigration demonstration left Belfast
OL,8,FCity Hall on Saturday. Three police
OL,9,Fofficers were injured in the
OL,10,Fdisturbances.
OL,12,FA number of men have been charged and
OL,13,Fappeared at Belfast Magistrates' Court
OL,14,Fon Monday.
OL,16,FDeputy District Judge Liam McStay said
OL,17,Fthere were racist elements to the
OL,18,Fviolence and that the message had to
OL,19,Fbe sent that if "you allow yourself to
OL,20,Fbecome involved in this you will be
OL,21,Fremanded".
